data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: A cartoon character is standing beside the door of a concrete house. He has short black hair and is extremely skinny. His appearance is quite like a human. To be more specific, he has blue skin and a sharp nose, and he has a rather large earlobe in which there is a yellow circle with a black spot in the center. Based on the observation, I guess he is probably an alien who comes from another world outside the earth. He is carrying a green square handbag in one hand while holding a mobile phone in the other. And he is also leading a big white bird whose neck is tied up with a string. Inside the house, there is a normal-looking adult man sitting on the couch. (127字)
